  "texts": [
    "Even though the performance of Bing Chat was comparatively low, our findings highlight the potential of chatbots for identifying different forms of false information in online environments.",
    "However, there is a strong imbalance concerning chatbots' performance in lower-resource languages (e.g.",
    "Ukrainian), as we see substantial performance drops and, in the case of Bing Chat, decrease in responsiveness.",
    "While lower performance in low resource languages can be expected based on earlier research (e.g.",
    "[29]), it raises concerns regarding the use of LLM-based chatbots for evaluating the veracity of information in contexts where false information is likely to be generated in non-English languages and when information accuracy is of paramount importance, such as in the case of the ongoing war in Ukraine."
  ],
